{
  "stem": "4247.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after a few days, I realized that it's not really safe for me to stay in there because the janitor was the, the totum factum there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know what totum factum is?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Uh-huh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He's the most important person, right?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The big potato there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I imagine, he started to wonder about Horvath Laszlo.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's there all day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I went out and presented myself for work as a toolmaker in one of the still working factories there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I worked there for short-- part-time-- short time only.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because, by that time, the Russians started to push in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Budapest, by that time, was surrounded.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the factory was a fair while out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I went there by streetcar.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after two, three weeks, it was not possible to safely get there and get home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "From that moment on, of course, the janitor realized that, you know, I cannot go out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was quite safe to stay in the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The Germans-- I mean, by that time, the-- to, to give you an idea, how I said to you earlier how important it is-- how important it is to, to look straight into somebody's eye in, in trying to salvage one's life.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "On the-- one, one, one of the last days when I was coming back from work from this Hungarian factory, I had to walk from the streetcar to Merleg utca 33, where I lived.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this factory had a library.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was taking home some books.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And as I was walking through-- it was a deserted street because it was already an open city.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not safe to walk on the streets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could hear cannons all over the place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Planes were coming, either Russians or Germans, either Ratas or Stukas, right?",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
